bilingual.source: Youth is the future of the nation.
This youth has a great talent for music.
bilingual.target: 这位青年在音乐方面很有天赋。

bilingual.source: She spent her youth traveling around the world.
bilingual.target: 她在青年时期环游了世界。

bilingual.source: This book tells the story of a youth growing up.
bilingual.target: 这本书讲述了一个青年的成长故事。

bilingual.source: He looks back on his youth with fond memories.
bilingual.target: 他怀着美好的回忆回顾他的青年时期。

bilingual.source: He is a warm blood youth, always full of passion.
bilingual.target: 他是一个热血青年，总是充满激情。

bilingual.source: Many youth like to participate in volunteer activities.
bilingual.target: 许多青年喜欢参加志愿者活动。

bilingual.source: Skateboarding is a prominent subculture among urban youth.
bilingual.target: 滑板是城市青年中显著的亚文化。

bilingual.source: The youth in our community are very active in volunteering.
bilingual.target: 我们社区的青年非常积极参与志愿服务。

bilingual.source: The government is launching initiatives to support dropout youth.
bilingual.target: 政府正在推出支持辍学者青年的计划。

list.abstract: 《YOUTH》是澳洲超人气新生代男歌手Troye Sivan（特洛耶·希文）演唱的一首歌曲。
YOUTH，是荣御乐器的民谣吉他品牌系列，旨在为年轻的吉他爱好者打造每一把优质的木吉他。

yingyinNormal.en: Can I stop going to the youth orchestra, then?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我能不去青年管弦乐团啦?

yingyinNormal.en: Or a, hookup as it's referred to by today's urban youth. Really? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者说，配对，现在的都市青年好像都这么说的。真的吗？是的。

yingyinNormal.en: No.No.No. The youth orchestra is a good thing. That shows you're a joiner-inner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不不，去青年管弦乐团是个好事儿，显示你有团体合作精神。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I'm ready. I don't know if Stuart told you what you're up against tonight, but before you stands the co-captain of the East Texas Christian Youth Holy Roller Bowling League championship team. Seven to 12 year old division. Also, Penny's pretty good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然准备好了。我不知道斯图尔特有没有告诉你今晚你的对手是谁，不过站在你面前的人就是东德克萨斯州青年基督徒圣保龄同盟会冠军队的联盟队长，7到12岁参赛组。佩妮打得也不错。

yingyinNormal.en: But by the time the human body has circled the sun 80 times, its youth and vigor are gone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但当人活到80，青春和活力就已不再。

yingyinNormal.en: Brilliant. It's so refreshing to talk to the youth of today. Our future's in bright hands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 了不起，和当今的年轻人谈话真让人耳目一新，我们的未来可期。

yingyinNormal.en: They were fun, though. In my youth, all the great hostesses used to have luncheon laid for 20 every day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但那多好玩啊，我年轻时，那些大宅子每天都摆下能招待二十人的午宴。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Tribbiani. Oh hi. Your generous contribution brings us a big step closer to building the youth center.
yingyinNormal.zh: 崔比亚尼先生，你的慷慨解囊，让兴建活动中心的事大有进展。

yingyinNormal.en: Peter Jason Quill, from Terra. Raised from youth by a band of mercenaries called the Ravagers, led by Yondu Udonta.
yingyinNormal.zh: 彼得杰森奎尔，来自地球，由一批称为破坏者的佣兵带大，领袖是勇度。

yingyinNormal.en: My pants are missing, I don't remember anything. Penny, this is your youth. What do I do? I don't know, check your body for tattoos?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的裤子不见了，我什么都不记得了。佩妮，你青春在断片中度过，分享下经验？我不知道，检查一下有没有新纹身吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I don't know why the kids need a youth center anyway. You know? They should just watch TV after school like I did and I turned out fine. Not great.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些小孩要活动中心干嘛？放了学跟我一样看电视就好了，我现在也蛮好的。但是不优秀。

yingyinNormal.en: Many visual beauty standards vary between cultures and eras, and signs of youth, fertility and good health, such as long lustrous hair, or smooth, scar-free skin, are almost always in demand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 视觉审美标准在各文化、时代之间皆相异，年轻、生育力与健康的征象也都不同，例如有光泽的长长秀发或光滑无痕的肌肤几乎总是需求不断。

examination_example.sentence: It deterred luxury consumers who found their expensive clothing more closely associated with working-class <highlight>youth</highlight> culture than a prestigious heritage fashion house.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它让奢侈品消费者望而却步，他们发现自己的昂贵服装与工人阶级青年文化的联系比其与享有盛誉的传统时装屋更密切相关。

sense_info_list.en: the time of life between being a child and an adult

examination_example.sentence: I wouldn't go back to the crippling self-consciousness of my <highlight>youth</highlight> if you paid me.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 即使你付钱给我，我也不会回到我年轻时那种极度自卑的状态。

examination_example.sentence: This is the age women start to become "invisible"—our value, attractiveness and power supposedly diminished by the vanishing of <highlight>youth</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是女性开始变得“隐形”的年龄—我们的价值、吸引力和力量据说会随着青春的消逝而减少。

examination_example.sentence: American <highlight>youth</highlight> are not going to the cinema nearly as often as they did in the past.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国年轻人现在不像过去那样经常去看电影了。

examination_example.sentence: For today's <highlight>youth</highlight>, books, newspapers and magazines have less and less of a presence in their daily lives.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于今天的年轻人来说，书籍、报纸和杂志在他们的日常生活中越来越少地出现。

examination_example.sentence: High-tech industries such as NASA's Jet Propulsion Laboratory have found that their best overall problem solvers were master tinkerers in their <highlight>youth</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国国家航空航天局的喷气推进实验室等高科技行业发现，他们最好的综合问题解决者是企业初创时期的能工巧匠。

word_usage.usage:
youth作为“青年”讲，指整体时，是一个集体名词，用单数形式，但谓语动词用复数：
The youth today are quite different from those a century ago.
现在的青年与一个世纪前的青年大不相同。

examination_example.sentence: If you're looking for cleanliness and a modern hostel, look no further than <highlight>Youth</highlight> Station.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你想找一家干净又现代化的旅馆，那就去青年旅社吧。

examination_example.sentence: Who is eligible: <highlight>Youth</highlight> 15-18 years old in select communities.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 符合条件者：特定社区15-18岁青年。

examination_example.sentence: You could apply to be a Stewardship <highlight>Youth</highlight> Ranger and work on local natural resource management projects for eight weeks this summer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你可以申请成为一名青年护林员，今年夏天参加为期8周的当地自然资源管理项目。

examination_example.sentence: If you'd like to build a powerful bond with your garden, start by taking some time to recall the gardens of your <highlight>youth</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你想和你的花园建立一种强烈的联系，那就从花点时间回忆你年轻时的花园开始。

examination_example.sentence: Video themes are about intellectually disabled <highlight>youth</highlight> and their parents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 视频主题是关于智障青少年和他们的父母。

examination_example.sentence: Zhu showed her greetings to China’s <highlight>youth</highlight> on this special occasion and shared her experience in life and career.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在这个特殊的时刻，朱向中国青年致以问候，并分享了她的生活和事业经历。

examination_example.sentence: After he won the May 4th Medal of Chinese <highlight>Youth</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他获得五四中国青年奖章后。

examination_example.sentence: The song The <highlight>Youth</highlight> tells people never to give up their dreams.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 《青春》这首歌告诉人们永远不要放弃他们的梦想。

examination_example.sentence: Then, he posted his first audiobook <highlight>Youth</highlight> Will Not Return on Qingting in 2016.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2016年他在《倾听》发布了他的第一本有声读物《青春一去不复回》。
